OL,7,FSir Keir has pledged to bring down net
OL,8,Fmigration; the number of people coming
OL,9,Fto UK from overseas, minus the number
OL,10,Fof people leaving.
OL,12,FIt hit a record high in 2022 at
OL,13,F745,000, before falling around 10 per
OL,14,Fcent last year.
OL,16,FHowever, net migration is still huge
OL,17,Fby historical standards at 685,000.
